{"data":[{"id":2,"documentId":"qtk88kedte40tclcgs35ij0d","title":"FOOD RESCUE DARI BISNIS MAKANAN","description":"Food rescue adalah upaya penyelamatan makanan surplus yang dihasilkan oleh industri hospitality dan bisnis makanan dari potensi terbuang.\n\n\nGarda Pangan menjalin kerja sama dengan mitra-mitra dari restoran, hotel, bakery, kafe, rumah makan, katering, ritel, distributor, FMCG, dan berbagai bisnis makanan lainnya yang berkomitmen mendonasikan makanan surplus layak makan yang dihasilkan. Food rescue dilakukan setiap harinya dengan menjemput makanan yang tidak terjual dari mitra untuk didistribusikan langsung secara door-to-door kepada masyarakat membutuhkan.","ctaLabel":"Selengkapknya","ctaLink":"/mitra","createdAt":"2026-05-16T07:56:45.079Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-16T07:56:45.079Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-16T07:56:45.141Z","thumbnail":{"id":23,"documentId":"r0atlk738rxdzjy8ralvx4qp","name":"7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4.png","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":526,"height":704,"formats":{"small":{"ext":".png","url":"https://promising-freedom-82afaec97e.media.strapiapp.com/small_7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4_8a3df03bc2.png","hash":"small_7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4_8a3df03bc2","mime":"image/png","name":"small_7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4.png","path":null,"size":466.68,"width":374,"height":500,"sizeInBytes":466684},"thumbnail":{"ext":".png","url":"https://promising-freedom-82afaec97e.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4_8a3df03bc2.png","hash":"thumbnail_7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4_8a3df03bc2","mime":"image/png","name":"thumbnail_7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4.png","path":null,"size":51.42,"width":117,"height":156,"sizeInBytes":51416}},"hash":"7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7def0f8b8eff20cc4_8a3df03bc2","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","size":207.53,"url":"https://promising-freedom-82afaec97e.media.strapiapp.com/7b48fcec3d8002b8935f88f7de